{"tid":1184391,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[live] 乜都冇plan十一日倫敦東歐","createTime":"2019-06-03T14:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T18:50:49.000Z","uid":110952,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"51553f7ccdfac8e22e0bb576c6857841829401c3","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T14:56:01.000Z","msg":"琴晚半夜買機票，而家係機場<br />\n啱啱book 左頭兩晚倫敦hostel <br />\n之後去邊都未諗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYpvRdZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYpvRdZ.jpg&h=ca9e1790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上機喇<br />\n德國佬好準時"},{"pid":"81fa728c19709c68b7e597b9e02b3481c1597bf0","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZdgNX6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdgNX6x.jpg&h=3e6157b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭a340 去法蘭克福轉機<br />\n呢程機有旅行團，好多唔識英文又好嘈既師奶呀叔，好彩帶哂耳塞眼罩<br />\n咁啱中間冇人坐，可以訓哂兩個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPstHzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPstHzv.jpg&h=fe1cb5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dMKfUB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dMKfUB.jpg&h=790c3cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwhat time is it ?<br />\n0545, 轉機唔駛出境，但都要security check <br />\ncheck 行李啲人面口好西，我前面個人分開擺electronic devices <br />\n佢好惡咁話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同事之前同你講既野你聽唔明咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7sJwt6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7sJwt6.jpg&h=8f27c928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好喇，而家去搭細機去London city airport<br />\n六點幾好多西裝友，咁早返工出差，諗起都攰，但係佢地睇落又好精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e913a63ac8c4f279e9ad5ff95a3db58e6fb2cb2e","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"到London <br />\n去hostel 擺底啲野先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7ese5X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7ese5X.jpg&h=c74161da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就算落雨都冇人擔遮<br />\n<br />\nhostel 係Earls Court station 附近<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sgt41Mu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgt41Mu.jpg&h=8ef7962f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家搵野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5599ab43f20ef217efb5f7abef1e81d176703fc","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"同hostel staff 講起早餐<br />\n佢話而家佢地唔興食traditional English breakfast, 太heavy 喇，要星期日先會食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHJMvMi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHJMvMi.jpg&h=56ce3ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其搵左間賣咖啡輕食既入去<br />\n<br />\n個package 上面個啲全部都係牛油，駛唔駛咁多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6DkAcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6DkAcx.jpg&h=4f9fd69d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8df6f9e8c06ce605afd5dcd8365a8353f25e0299","tid":1184391,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5599ab43f20ef217efb5f7abef1e81d176703fc","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"同hostel staff 講起早餐<br />\n佢話而家佢地唔興食traditional English breakfast, 太heavy 喇，要星期日先會食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHJMvMi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHJMvMi.jpg&h=56ce3ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其搵左間賣咖啡輕食既入去<br />\n<br />\n個package 上