T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"我知啊不過我夾唔到，我七月尾就返香港...<br />\n好遺憾冇得睇"},{"pid":"759a113c723aa92a5022fc459e8e6024399e60da","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T08:01:03.000Z","msg":"啱啱訓醒，煩緊聽日去邊，聽日住宿都未book <br />\n去布拉格好冇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日凍得滯，走去唐人街食個pho 先<br />\n好好食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw, 一芳開到黎倫敦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSUTicA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSUTicA.jpg&h=2814dd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住去左買對Dr Martens, 99磅<br />\n<br />\n坐英國啲巴士上層都可以好似係香港咁，扮渣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c48Qkr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc48Qkr2.jpg&h=f96d9b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚去睇呢套<br />\neverybody is talking about Jamie<br />\n青春musical 咁喇<br />\n講一個十六歲既男仔想成為Drag Queen<br />\n主角唱得一般遮&hellip;反而呀媽唱得好動人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GfbPk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GfbPk6.jpg&h=b00ce885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續搵聽日去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe857d087083a447fd3bc24a6cf7424f9be7cbc","tid":1184391,"uid":108674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f8825b8b74815a9bbbc411b10bb63c388691d4","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"買完飛想去the national gallery 行下<br />\n入左去發覺離離去去都係人像<br />\n心諗，唔通做緊主題展<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇真啲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqwFA58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqwFA58.jpg&h=c0cc8bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nnational <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">portrait</span> gallery <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDaCDjT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDaCDjT.jpg&h=7cac8a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有反侵侵遊行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2FjDnMH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2FjDnMH.jpg&h=bc119d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:35:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e1e9b240b4564a155d87a269189b484ccd53b7","tid":1184391,"uid":108674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T09:48:42.000Z","msg":"如果住hostel又有廚具 <br />\n可以係超市買青口自己煮<br />\n平靚正"},{"pid":"59ca06baae3fe533e705d19b9eba3d7ed64a2186","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:46:45.000Z","msg":"趁delay 寫下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nday 2 都係jet lag 得好勁，一早醒左，食完野又訓到一點先出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去搵啲野食先喇 ，去左borough market<br />\n係大型乾濕貨市集，日日都有<br />\n啲生蠔扺食，大概2&pound;一個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZfLuy8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZfLuy8.jpg&h=ee43e008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGSRp7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGSRp7B.jpg&h=773c7793&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1QGNkX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1QGNkX.jpg&h=b601e623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyGbp7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyGbp7u.jpg&h=f3971dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FH39bNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFH39bNw.jpg&h=5e0c4f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ek81NkT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEk81NkT.jpg&h=0d7649c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCTX47z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCTX47z.jpg&h=aff378f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecEMd2V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecEMd2V.jpg&h=1067c11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再行一陣，係Soho 食左個龍蝦包，仆你個街要14&pound;, 係好食既但都唔值<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkfRPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkfRPO.jpg&h=c893fc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1dEy29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1dEy29.jpg&h=50e6d83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢晚就睇les mis 喇！<br />\n山頂位，但都睇得哂個舞台，佢啲過場同舞台設計真係好正<br />\n演員都好專業，唯一個敗筆係Cosette大個版竟然搵左個黑人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係歧視&hellip;但真係好出戲，個角色係金髮白人，細個牌個妹妹都仲係白人，大個變左黑人 做乜9呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e813f73688b275c5b9e50c837e63da5c1db557d","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:23:19.000Z","msg":"day 3 - London<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住呢日走，但一路都揸唔止主意去邊<br />\n咁就出事喇，當晚啲機票已經好貴(但買之後既重貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，咁諗諗下都係留多日<br />\n<br />\n首先去左British museum, 做緊個關於漫畫既專題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AoLb9D6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAoLb9D6.jpg&h=c960d9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiOUnY2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiOUnY2.jpg&h=fbf5808c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHJMYxp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHJMYxp.jpg&h=efcac966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後去左東區 brick lane 行下vintage 店<br />\n冇啱我既碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OG6Zn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OG6Zn7.jpg&h=552e7d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8T9cH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8T9cH9.jpg&h=1e025955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsLC53b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsLC53b.jpg&h=04e0f83d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c52564cf09fc3dd3c13597ee095f0793dbf96487","tid":1184391,"uid":6378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c2eedd59130e62c9f746d079ff3ecbacec7e172","tid":1184391,"uid":110952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64605bd3bad970dfe5ae08bcdbb77e893caf4c8","tid":1184391,"uid":248166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"點解去完london係去東歐唔係去西歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw les miserables好睇到癲，睇咗兩次<br />\n利申：住london"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"因爲張機票係Vienna 走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知咁樣好唔順路...<br />\n係夾硬加London 落去<br />\n因爲想黎睇musical <br />\n<br />\n有冇好食推介？<br />\n想食青口，但得一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T00:22:26.000Z","msg":"食啦 我係巴塞叫左兜青口<br />\n然後先醒起個friend唔食得<br />\n自己一個食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8943f32c5b5dda2b296d65f422a072630f65f310","tid":1184391,"uid":82018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite